<div id="review_3430683806" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3430683806" />
    <a title="Peter Wassam" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/92003485-peter-wassam"><img alt="Peter Wassam" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3430683806?book_show_action=true">Aug 02, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Peter Wassam" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Peter Wassam" href="/user/show/92003485-peter-wassam">Peter Wassam</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3430683806" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14256549742186379527">Wow wow wow wow wow. The greatest person the USA has ever produced, and I say that as an atheist about a minister. I&apos;m shocked more than anything by how wide-ranging his knowledge was- philosophy, arts, politics, sociology, history. There&apos;s never a misplaced word or phrase. What a guy. </span>
  <span id="freeText14256549742186379527" style="display:none">Wow wow wow wow wow. The greatest person the USA has ever produced, and I say that as an atheist about a minister. I'm shocked more than anything by how wide-ranging his knowledge was- philosophy, arts, politics, sociology, history. There's never a misplaced word or phrase. What a guy. </span>
  <a data-text-id="14256549742186379527" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

