        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer45129426" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14918519473560398140">One of the most treasured books in my library, &apos;A Testament of Hope&apos; is a challenging, provocative, and hopeful anthology of writings from the pen of Martin Luther King Jr. &apos;Letter from Birmingham Jail&apos; is included, along with excerpts from &apos;Why We Can&apos;t Wait,&apos; popular speeches, and interviews with various publications. <br/><br/>King&apos;s capacious mind and fierce courage remain unmatched. His understanding of Christianity was transcendent in all the ways that matter. Today&apos;s Evangelicals remain clueless. A</span>
  <span id="freeText14918519473560398140" style="display:none">One of the most treasured books in my library, 'A Testament of Hope' is a challenging, provocative, and hopeful anthology of writings from the pen of Martin Luther King Jr. 'Letter from Birmingham Jail' is included, along with excerpts from 'Why We Can't Wait,' popular speeches, and interviews with various publications. <br /><br />King's capacious mind and fierce courage remain unmatched. His understanding of Christianity was transcendent in all the ways that matter. Today's Evangelicals remain clueless. A white person can never really understand the black struggle, but I don't think anyone who confronts it can diminish the importance of emancipation, equality, and a continuuing program of civil rights for all.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14918519473560398140" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

